title: XIQ Radio Information
agents: special
catalog: hw/network/wifi
license: free
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the individual radio interfaces (2.4 GHz, 5 GHz,
 6 GHz) of an ExtremeCloudIQ Access Point. It extracts:
  - Radio operational state
  - Channel and channel width
  - Transmit power
  - Number of clients per radio
 .
 The state is determined as follows:
  - OK: Radio enabled and operational
  - WARN: Radio enabled but reporting degraded condition
  - CRIT: Radio disabled although AP is online
  - UNKNOWN: Radio information missing

item:
 A combination of Access Point name and radio band
 (e.g. "AP1234 5GHz").

perfdata:
 Provides client count per radio band.
